      "description": "Unified thinking configuration for all providers.\n\nReplaces both TS EffortLevel and ThinkingConfig: TS EffortLevel ('low'|'medium'|'high'|'max') → ThinkingLevel::low()/medium()/high()/xhigh() TS ThinkingConfig { type: 'enabled', N }     → ThinkingLevel { effort: Medium, budget: Some(N) } TS ThinkingConfig { type: 'disabled' }       → ThinkingLevel::none()\n\nOnly 2 typed fields (effort + budget_tokens) are universal across providers. All provider-specific thinking params go through `options` (data-driven passthrough).",
